quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  74,32,Haa dhorgamu! Ji'attin kakadha
  74,33,Halkaniinis; yeroo inni deeme
  74,34,Bariidhaanis yeroo inni ife
  74,35,"Dhugumatti, isheen (saqar) tokkoo (rakkoolee) gurgurddooti"
  74,36,Namaaf akeekkachiiftuudha
  74,37,"Nama isin irraa (hojii gaariidhaan) fuulduratti deemuu, yookiin duubatti hafuu fedheef (akeekkachiistuu dha)"
  74,38,Lubbuun hundi waan hojjatteen qabamtuudha
  74,39,Warra mirgaa malee
  74,40,(Isaan) jannata keessatti wal gaggaafatu
  74,41,Yakkamtoota irraa (wal gaafatu)
  74,42,"Maaltu Saqariin keessa isin seensise?\" (isaanin jedhu)"
  74,43,"Ni jedhan: \"nuti warra salaatan irraa hin turre"
  74,44,Hiyyeeyyii kan nyaachifnus hin turre
  74,45,Warra (hamtuu) keessa seenuu wajjin seenaa turre
  74,46,Guyyaa mindaas kan sobsiifnu turre
  74,47,"Hanga (duuti) mirkanaayaan nutti dhufutti (haala kana irra turre)\" (jedhu)"
  74,48,Jaarsummaan (araarri) warra araarsanii isaan hin fayyadu
  74,49,Maaltu isaaniif jiraayi gorsa (Qur'aanaa) irraa gara galoo ta'u
  74,50,(Yeroo akeekkachiisa Rabbii irraa dheessan) akka harree diidoo dammaqanii (gugatanii) fakkaatu
  74,51,Leenca irraa kan baqatan
  74,52,Inumaa namni isaan irraa ta'e hundi kitaabota banamoo kennamuu fedha
  74,53,"Dhugumatti, (hin kennamanu) isaan Aakhirumaayyuu hin sodaatanu"
  74,54,"Dhugumatti, inni (Qur'aanni) gorsa"
  74,55,Nama fedheetu isaan gorfama
  74,56,Yoo Rabbiin fedhe malee hin gorfamanuInni (Rabbiin) kan sodaatamuu haqa godhatuufi Abbaa Araaramaati